QuestData.Title: Wiggletail's Poking Fork
QuestData.Description:
<The tenacious tine of the vanquished prince.
It does not thrum with any power whatsoever. In fact, it appears quite plain, and a bit rusted.
You pocket it anyway. Perhaps Finder Palta would be interested?>
QuestData.LogDescription: Show Wiggletail's Poking Fork to Finder Palta in Newhome in Nazjatar.
